OL,3,C`I thought I was in the room with the
OL,4,Cdevil': Domestic abuse victim speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FA domestic abuse survivor has broken
OL,8,Fher silence to reveal the chilling
OL,9,Freality of what a victim endures.
OL,11,FWanita McCrea spoke to UTV just days
OL,12,Fafter her abuser, former partner Keith
OL,13,FHenry, was finally jailed after
OL,14,Fabandoning an appeal to his sentence.
OL,16,FThe 52-year-old, from Tulnacross Road,
OL,17,FCookstown, had been on bail pending
OL,18,Fthe appeal. He's now in prison after a
OL,19,Fjudge warned he could face a longer
OL,20,Fspell behind bars.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772719872
OL,3,C`I thought I was in the room with the
OL,4,Cdevil': Domestic abuse victim speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FAfter deliberating with his legal
OL,8,Fteam, Henry accepted the original 12-
OL,9,Fmonth sentence handed down to him, to
OL,10,Fbe spent between custody and licence.
OL,12,FHe was also given a restraining order.
OL,14,FLast spring, the 52-year-old was
OL,15,Fconvicted of a number of domestic-
OL,16,Fabuse related crimes including assault
OL,17,Fand non-fatal strangulation.
OL,19,FWanita told UTV: "He will be known as
OL,20,Fa domestic abuser for the rest of his
OL,21,Flife and that is justice for me.''
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
