FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772719872
OL,3,C`I thought I was in the room with the
OL,4,Cdevil': Domestic abuse victim speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FShe will never forget the moment he
OL,8,Ftried to strangle her.
OL,10,F"He was restricting my airways and I
OL,11,Fwas not able to breathe.
OL,13,F"In my panic, fight or flight, my arms
OL,14,Fwere going, I thought my head was
OL,15,Fgoing to explode.
OL,17,F"I thought this was the end for me.''
OL,19,FHenry then suddenly let go.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
