PN,44304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772719872
OL,3,C`I thought I was in the room with the
OL,4,Cdevil': Domestic abuse victim speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FWanita managed to record the
OL,8,Fterrifying attack on her mobile phone.
OL,9,FIt would later prove crucial evidence
OL,10,Fin the case against her ex.
OL,12,FUTV listened to the recording. It is
OL,13,Fharrowing and distressing and suddenly
OL,14,Fends with an angry Henry telling
OL,15,FWanita "I will strangle you".
OL,17,FWanita said: "Honestly the way I can
OL,18,Fdescribe it is, you know that, you
OL,19,Fswear you were in the room with the
OL,20,Fdevil, well I was. I thought I was
OL,21,Fgoing to die that night.''
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
