OL,3,C`I thought I was in the room with the
OL,4,Cdevil': Domestic abuse victim speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FNon-fatal strangulation is a
OL,8,Frelatively new offence in Northern
OL,9,FIreland. It is a crime viewed as a red
OL,10,Fflag for esclating violence in a
OL,11,Frelationship.
OL,13,FIn the magistrates' court where Henry
OL,14,Fwas convicted, the maximum sentence is
OL,15,Ftwo years.
OL,17,FIn the higher crown court, it can be
OL,18,Fup to 14 years for perpetrators.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
