PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772719872
OL,3,C`I thought I was in the room with the
OL,4,Cdevil': Domestic abuse victim speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FThere have been thousands of arrests
OL,8,Ffor non-fatal strangulation since it
OL,9,Fwas brought into force.
OL,11,FThere are concerns however that
OL,12,Fcharges and convictions are not at the
OL,13,Flevel they could be.
OL,15,FHundreds of cases are currently under
OL,16,Fconsideration for potential charges.
OL,18,FFor Wanita, her only regret is not
OL,19,Fleaving the two-year relationship
OL,20,Fsooner. But she has message for others.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
