OL,3,C`I thought I was in the room with the
OL,4,Cdevil': Domestic abuse victim speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F"Pack a little bag with your personal
OL,8,Fstuff, get out and go straight to the
OL,9,Fpolice,'' she said.
OL,11,FIf you have been affected by issues
OL,12,Fraised you can contact the National
OL,13,FDomestic Abuse Helpline on 0808 2000
OL,14,F247 or Women's Aid Federation NI on
OL,15,F028 9024 9041.
OL,17,FGeneral advice and helplines can also
OL,18,Fbe found here.
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,21,FITVX
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/8
